page.content: {These trees are found in Church Wood: Beech,Common Lime,Spanish Chestnut, Horse Chestnut,Sycamore,Goat Willow, Hazel,Oak,Ash,Mountin Ash or Rowan, Hawthorn or May,Holly,Elm,Ivy,Laurel, Scots Pine,Spruce,Larch,Elderberry,Red Cedar,Douglas Fir,Field Maple,Silver Birch.{These wild flowers are found {too:}Snowdrop,Primrose,Enchanters Nig- htshade,Red Campion,Foxglove,Bluebell, Violet,Dog Rose,Nettle,Arum Lily,Wall- Pennywort,Herb Robert,Lesser Willow Herb,Ivy Leaved Toad Flax,Bramble,Ch- arlock,Buttercup,Narrow Leaved Vetch, Wood Avens,Yellow Pimpernel,Marsh Th- istle,Common Cat Ears,Nipple Wort,Wi- ld Celery,Yarrow,Ground Ivy,Great Bi- nd Weed,Shepherds Purse,Germander,Sp- well,Daisy,White Clover,Woody Nights- hade,Fumitory,Chamomile,Hedge Parsley, Wood Woundwort,and Yellow Meadow Vetch.
